and unwavering.

116
00:19:58,096 --> 00:19:59,927
Unwavering.

117
00:20:01,833 --> 00:20:03,494
What's that?

118
00:20:05,604 --> 00:20:10,507
Leave me alone with this man,
gentlemen.

119
00:20:20,953 --> 00:20:24,320
What have you -

120
00:20:42,975 --> 00:20:46,103
Very well. You can go.

121
00:20:46,445 --> 00:20:48,743
No, wait!

122
00:22:07,526 --> 00:22:10,495
Hands up...
if anyone's there!

123
00:22:13,765 --> 00:22:15,232
Is anyone there?

124
00:22:18,570 --> 00:22:20,231
There's no one here.

125
00:22:21,173 --> 00:22:24,370
We can hold the wedding here
safe enough.

126
00:23:22,734 --> 00:23:26,727
- Bill Lawgen
- And Mary Syer

127
