You see the moon over Soho?

132
00:24:00,205 --> 00:24:02,673
I see it, dearest.

133
00:24:05,010 --> 00:24:09,538
Do you feel my heart beating,
my beloved?

134
00:24:10,615 --> 00:24:13,083
I feel it, my darling.

135
00:24:14,753 --> 00:24:19,713
Wherever you go,
I too shall go.

136
00:24:20,992 --> 00:24:24,018
And wherever you are...

137
00:24:24,229 --> 00:24:29,690
I want to be too

138
00:24:30,669 --> 00:24:36,630
And though there's no license
from city hall

139
00:24:37,909 --> 00:24:43,814
And no altar
covered with flowers fair

140
00:24:44,449 --> 00:24:50,820
And though you may not know
where your gown came from

141
