No, no.
Stay a while, Reverend.

148
00:27:03,521 --> 00:27:04,954
Attention, everyone!

149
00:27:05,890 --> 00:27:07,915
It's ten past 2:00!

150
00:27:37,155 --> 00:27:41,455
Hip, hip, hurray!

151
